      <title>日本首相的困境引发了对潜在继任者的猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/who-s-waiting-in-the-wings-as-japan-s-premier-kishida-flounders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄的任期可能屈指可数，最近的一项民意调查显示，绝大多数选民希望这位陷入困境的领导人最迟在 9 月份任期结束前辞去首相职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/who-s-waiting-in-the-wings-as-japan-s-premier-kishida-flounders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国计划对价值 290 亿美元的陆桥项目进行全球招标，以绕过马六甲海峡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/thailand-plans-global-bidding-for-29-billion-project-to-bypass-malacca-strait</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国计划对一个耗资 1 万亿泰铢（合 290 亿美元）的项目进行国际竞标，该项目旨在绕过马六甲海峡，大幅缩短印度洋和太平洋之间的航运时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/thailand-plans-global-bidding-for-29-billion-project-to-bypass-malacca-strait</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:29:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称两个中国气球越过关键分隔线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/taiwan-says-two-chinese-balloons-crossed-key-separating-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾表示，两个中国气象气球越过美国几十年前为缓解两国紧张关系而划定的海峡线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/taiwan-says-two-chinese-balloons-crossed-key-separating-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:18:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于利率暂停缓解压力，澳大利亚总理的民调反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/australian-pm-s-polling-rebounds-as-rate-pause-eases-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济价格压力有降温迹象，本月早些时候储备银行维持利率不变，澳大利亚工党政府在民意调查中重新领先于中右翼反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/australian-pm-s-polling-rebounds-as-rate-pause-eases-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 02:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国总统安保车队发生碰撞 拜登安然无恙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/president-biden-s-security-motorcade-involved-in-collision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一辆汽车与特拉华州威尔明顿总统乔·拜登安保人员的一辆汽车相撞，但总统没有受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/president-biden-s-security-motorcade-involved-in-collision</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 01:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜批评美韩核谈判并发射洲际弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/north-korea-fires-suspected-ballistic-missile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在批评美国和韩国就遏制平壤核野心举行会谈后，朝鲜向其东海岸附近海域发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹，以挑衅性地展示武力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/north-korea-fires-suspected-ballistic-missile</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 23:44:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚旅游热点地区发生洪水导致人们陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/australia-floods-update-queeensland-issues-warning-cairns-airport-closes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[热带气旋过后，连日降雨，澳大利亚最北部的一个重要旅游区被洪水淹没，危及生命。]]></description>
